    <item>
      <title>会见将决定唐纳德·特朗普命运的曼哈顿陪审团</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/meet-the-manhattan-jury-that-will-decide-donald-trump-s-fate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约选出了 12 名陪审员参加唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的刑事审判，这位前总统被指控在 2016 年大选前伪造商业记录以掩盖性丑闻。选择陪审团是一个艰巨的过程：Juan Merchan 法官、检察官和辩护律师在三天内审查了近 200 名潜在陪审员，以剔除可能存在某种偏见的人。大多数被原谅的人表示他们不公平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/meet-the-manhattan-jury-that-will-decide-donald-trump-s-fate</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 13:12:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗“抵抗轴心”监视以色列并等待指挥</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/iran-s-axis-of-resistance-watches-israel-and-waits-for-command</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朋友和邻居说，本月早些时候，卡姆勒·阿尔-亚西尼本应陪同一位朋友前往大马士革的一家老人临终关怀医院，两人都在那里做志愿者，但她改变了主意，留在家里照顾残疾的儿子。这个决定让他们付出了生命的代价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/iran-s-axis-of-resistance-watches-israel-and-waits-for-command</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克罗地亚最高法院禁止总统米拉诺维奇担任总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/croat-top-court-bars-president-milanovic-from-becoming-premier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克罗地亚最高法院禁止总统佐兰·米拉诺维奇成为该国下一任总理，称他违反了宪法禁止现任国家元首在议会选举期间参与政治的规定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/croat-top-court-bars-president-milanovic-from-becoming-premier</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 12:57:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟因西岸暴力行为制裁数名以色列定居者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/eu-sanctions-several-israeli-settlers-over-violence-in-west-bank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟周五正式批准对暴力的以色列定居者实施制裁，这一程序步骤需要数周的技术工作，因为欧盟试图平衡对以色列的支持与解决加沙日益恶化的人道主义危机的需要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/eu-sanctions-several-israeli-settlers-over-violence-in-west-bank</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 12:20:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管面临压力，欧洲央行仍坚持对银行股息采取强硬立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/ecb-sticks-with-tough-line-on-bank-dividends-despite-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于强硬派和新任监事会主席克劳迪娅·布赫(Claudia Buch)的反对，高级监管机构试图软化欧洲央行对贷方股息和股票回购的立场，但这一努力却步履蹒跚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/ecb-sticks-with-tough-line-on-bank-dividends-despite-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 12:18:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔投票似曾相识，新兴市场债券反弹经过考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/top-emerging-market-bond-rally-tested-in-deja-vu-ecuador-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年新兴市场的最佳反弹取决于一个人的受欢迎程度：36 岁的香蕉财富继承人丹尼尔·诺博亚 (Daniel Noboa)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/top-emerging-market-bond-rally-tested-in-deja-vu-ecuador-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 11:58:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列对伊朗空军基地进行有限无人机袭击以回击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/iran-acknowledges-drone-attack-by-israel-and-says-it-failed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，以色列周五早上对伊朗进行了反击，在一次无人机行动中袭击了一个军事地点，但规模有限，似乎造成的损失很小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/iran-acknowledges-drone-attack-by-israel-and-says-it-failed</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 09:47:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列争论报道的对伊朗的袭击是否足够大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/israel-debates-if-reported-iran-attack-is-strong-enough-message</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于以色列对周五对伊朗的报复性袭击保持官方沉默，其分析人士和官员对此次袭击的规模是强弱的标志进行了权衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/israel-debates-if-reported-iran-attack-is-strong-enough-message</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 08:43:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪在印度世界最大的选举中竞选第三个任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/india-elections-day-1-voting-in-world-s-largest-democracy-begins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近10亿印度人周五开始在持续六周多的选举中投票，权衡是否给予总理纳伦德拉·莫迪第三个五年任期，以继续其经济和印度教民族主义政策的混合政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/india-elections-day-1-voting-in-world-s-largest-democracy-begins</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
